Heroku setup

- create accoaunt on heroku.

- create application

- how to setup heroku in existing project 



heroku login

heroku git:remote -a crop-monitor
git push heroku master
heroku run rake db:create
heroku run rake db:migrate
heroku run rake db:seed

crop-monitor.herokuapps.com

git add .
git add file1 file2
git commit -m 'msg'
git push heroku master

heroku run rake db:create
heroku run rake db:migrate
heroku run rake db:seed

